reviewText: ;Watched everything from series 1 - 32.  it is a good story.

This is a series I have been following for quite some time.  The only issue I have is that it is not yet published on american DVDs.  Or if you find one that is in the American format, it is very expensive.  It is cheaper just to be a DVD Player that plays all regions.

Fits in just fine to continue my Library of this Show, did not like the large warning label on cover of the Product, I see no need for this for those of us that understand the Region codes of the DVD World and have the proper equipment to view such discs.

These are outstanding movies. Hope 20 & 30 comes out soon.
Thank you for selling these.
